Submitted By:            (still-image rewrite based on blfs svt_av1_build_fix)
Date:                    2025-03-20
Initial Package Version: 1.21.2
Upstream Status:         Not submitted
Origin:                  Rewrite of libheif/plugins/encoder_svt.cc to implement
                         proper SVT-AV1 still image encoding per AVIF spec and
                         SVT-AV1 >= 1.0 API. Replaces build-fix-only patch with
                         full still-image-correct implementation.
Description:             - Fixes SVT-AV1 >= 1.0 API incompatibilities (renamed
                           structs/enums, changed init signature).
                         - Adds proper still image mode: intra_period_length=-1,
                           force_key_frames=1, enable_tpl_la=0, hierarchical_levels=0.
                         - Ensures AVIF 'still image' brand (mif1/avif), not sequence.
                         - Correct single-frame EOS flush.
                         - Removes video-oriented parameters irrelevant for stills.

